			"flow": [
				[
					"I would suggest you put Mrs. Parker under close scrutiny. Whenever men vanish under suspicious circumstances in this town, she is never far. The Sheriff said Jack was found behind the saloon? We couldn’t prove that she killed her seven husbands back in the day, but maybe we can prove her involvement this time."
